data.description: Discover the allure of this 4BD, 3BA lakefront haven with mesmerizing water views! The main ensuite is an oasis, featuring vaulted ceilings, an elegant claw-foot tub, expansive double shower, & dual sink vanity, along with a second ensuite downstairs. The kitchen, a chef's dream, boasts stainless steel appliances, & granite countertops with spacious pull-up bar seating. The open floor plan, complemented by newer luxury vinyl, leads to a cozy living room with a gas fireplace. Upstairs, a captivating loft bathed in natural light awaits is perfect for a sitting room or office. Step outside to a private retreat with a 6-year-old saltwater pool, landscaped yard, & waterfront gazebo. A sizeable dock that is perfect for launching a boat or fishing. Two sheds offer storage for gardening & pool essentials. Additional highlights include a durable metal roof, a covered front deck, Hardie board siding, and ample parking for an RV or boat. This isn't just a home; it's a lifestyle waiting for you.
